# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Pipeline stage tests — Arajet (PUJ), group B (price 148)
# Expected strategy per passenger count (live thresholds as of 2026-05-30):
#   ≤ 198 pax  → single-hotel          (un hotel cubre todo)
#   199–230    → multi-hotel            (varios hoteles, mismo IATA PUJ)
#   231+       → expansion-multi primero (grupos expandidos, mismo IATA)
#   luego      → overflow-multi         (PUJ + SDQ, grupo primario)
#   ≥ 290      → expansion-overflow-multi (PUJ + SDQ, grupos expandidos)
# Respuesta puede incluir "warnings" si hubo expansión u overflow.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Stage 1 — single-hotel (2 pax, debe devolver strategy: single-hotel)
POST http://127.0.0.1:5001/recommendations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "passengers": 500,
  "airline": "Arajet (PUJ)",
  "destination": "Arajet (PUJ)"
}

### Stage 1 — single-hotel con fechas (activa meal_relevance)
POST http://127.0.0.1:5001/recommendations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "passengers": 200,
  "airline": "Arajet (PUJ)",
  "destination": "Arajet (PUJ)",
